description:
Welcome to Season 9 of the Ultra Hardcore series. Season 9 has 20 participants split into 5 teams of 4. The map is randomly generated with a bedrock border around its 2000x2000 perimeter. The goal is to be the first team to kill the enderdragon. Only 3 ender eyes are needed to open the portal at the center of the map.

The only way to recover health in this is with golden apples or instant health potions. Golden apples require a 8 gold ingots (instead of nuggets) and an apple to craft. Glistering Melons require 1 gold block (instead of 1 nugget) and a melon. Health does not recover from keeping your hunger bar full.

(The Teams)
